data.description: Get away to your very own Hollow/Holler! Sitting in this simple, 3 bedroom house - you sit in the beautiful basin of a ridge that wraps around almost, completely-enclosing the property in a bowl. The 21 acres provide privacy and beauty. There may be potential for siting another house on the property.   The existing house can provide a temporary home base as the long-term, ultimate house is built.  From the North boundary to the Cumberland River.  The property once hosted a goat farm and a prohibition era still. The house is being sold as-is
